Coconut Ice Cream
   -chocolate covered Katie

2 c canned coconut milk
1/4 c + 1 tbsp sweetener of choice
1/8 tsp salt
1 1/2 tsp vanilla
optional ingredients for desired flavor

Combine all ingredients together (minus optionals) and transfer to an ice cream maker. Follow instructions from maker's manufacturer.

Notes: use full fat canned coconut milk, not lite or beverage. Sweeteners that work include pure maple syrup, sugar, coconut sugar, honey, agave, brown sugar, or xylitol for sugar free.
